reviewText:
Great videos!
They arrived just when they were supposed to!
This was gift for a party and it was a hit.
this is just a hoot!  but be warned it is sexually explicit.  It shows the sexual behavior of several animals.

These two DVDs cover all four episodes of Sex In The Wild which is four hours of animal reproduction challenges in the wild.

CAUTION: Not a family documentary unless you have already discussed and analyzed with your young ones about Adam and Eve from the biology side of the spectrum thoroughly and completely.

The sex organs of some animals are more than twenty five percent of their body length. To survive in the wild, shorter pregnancy periods of four weeks are as essential as the shape and length of male anatomy in fertilizing the egg as well as the shape of the sperm in reaching their destination, especially in the hot deserts of Africa and Australia. Very educational documentary since you get to witness biology in animals which is rarely ever documented in such settings for so many different type of creatures in so many different part of the planet earth. Birth could not be anymore astonishing on land or in water. Bravo, bravo, bravo.
